nodeTraining.title: Mock field Training programme on inspection for Internal Control System-ICS Group) conducted by the Team from MSOCB under the supervision of Shri Dorairaj K., Consultant Organic certification on the 15th March 2024

body.processed: The field inspection to an ICS group under the facilitation of the Directorate of Horticulture, Government of Meghalaya was conducted on the 15th March 2024 as part of the capacity building to the staff of MSOCB.
